#. Tag: title
#: details-search.docbook:11
#, no-c-format
msgid "Search Transactions"
msgstr "Iskanje transakcij"

#. Tag: para
#: details-search.docbook:13
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can use the <guilabel>Search transactions</guilabel> dialog to search "
"your data for transactions based on criteria that you specify. You can "
"access the dialog by selecting the <menuchoice> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Find transaction...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item, or "
"typing <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; &Shift;<keycap>F</keycap></"
"keycombo>."
msgstr ""
"Pogovorno okno <guilabel>Išči transakcije</guilabel> lahko uporabite za "
"iskanje podatkov za transakcije na podlagi meril, ki jih podate. Do "
"pogovornega okna lahko dostopate tako, da izberete menijsko postavko "
"<menuchoice> <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Poišči transakcijo...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> ali vtipkate <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; "
"&Shift;<keycap>F</keycap></keycombo>."

#. Tag: para
#: details-search.docbook:21
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There are two main tabs in this dialog. The <guilabel>Criteria</guilabel> "
"tab displays a number of subtabs for specifying the search criteria. When "
"the <guibutton>Find</guibutton> button is pressed, the search is initiated "
"and all criteria that have been entered on any of the Criteria subtabs will "
"be taken into account."
msgstr ""
"V tem pogovornem oknu sta dva glavna zavihka. Zavihek <guilabel>Kriterij</"
"guilabel> prikazuje številne podzavihke za določanje iskalnih kriterijev. Ko "
"pritisnete gumb <guibutton>Najdi</guibutton>, se začne iskanje in upoštevajo "
"se vsi kriteriji, ki so bili vneseni na katerem koli od podzavihkov "
"Kriteriji."

#. Tag: para
#: details-search.docbook:29
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"After the search has completed, the results will be displayed under the "
"<guilabel>Result</guilabel> tab. Below the list of results, &kmymoney; shows "
"the number of transactions that met the search criteria. Double-clicking an "
"individual transaction in the result list will bring up the appropriate "
"ledger with that transaction selected."
msgstr ""
"Ko je iskanje končano, bodo rezultati prikazani pod zavihkom "
"<guilabel>Rezultat</guilabel>. Pod seznamom rezultatov &kmymoney; prikazuje "
"število transakcij, ki izpolnjujejo iskalne kriterije. Dvoklik na posamezno "
"transakcijo na seznamu rezultatov bo prikazal ustrezno glavno knjigo z "
"izbrano transakcijo."

#. Tag: para
#: details-search.docbook:37
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guibutton>Reset</guibutton> button resets all of the fields on all of "
"the criteria subtabs back to the defaults. This allows you to specify new "
"search criteria."
msgstr ""
"Gumb <guibutton>Ponastavi</guibutton> ponastavi vsa polja na vseh "
"podzavihkih kriterijev nazaj na privzete vrednosti. To vam omogoča, da "
"določite nove iskalne kriterije."

#. Tag: para
#: details-search.docbook:43
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guibutton>Close</guibutton> button closes the <guilabel>Search "
"Transactions</guilabel> dialog box."
msgstr ""
"Gumb <guibutton>Zapri</guibutton> zapre pogovorno okno <guilabel>Iskanje "
"transakcij</guilabel>."

#. Tag: title
#: details-search.docbook:48
#, no-c-format
msgid "Search Criteria"
msgstr "Kriteriji iskanja"

#. Tag: para
#: details-search.docbook:49
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There are several subtabs under the main Criteria tab, each of which allows "
"you to specify a different type of search criteria. Below the area for "
"specifying the criteria, &kmymoney; lists each of the different types of "
"criteria that are currently specified for the search."
msgstr ""
"Pod glavnim zavihkom Kriteriji je več podzavihkov, od katerih vam vsak "
"omogoča, da določite drugačno vrsto iskalnih kriterijev. Pod območjem za "
"določanje kriterijev &kmymoney; navaja vsako od različnih vrst kriterijev, "
"ki so trenutno določeni za iskanje."

#. Tag: title
#: details-search.docbook:56
#, no-c-format
msgid "Text"
msgstr "Besedilo"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: details-search.docbook:58
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>search transactions, criteria tab, text subtab</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>iskanje transakcij, zavihek kriterijev, podzavihek besedilo</"
"screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: details-search.docbook:64
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>search transactions, criteria tab, text subtab</phrase>"
msgstr ""
"<phrase>iskanje transakcij, zavihek kriterijev, podzavihek besedilo</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: details-search.docbook:69
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This tab allows you to specify text to search for. There are also a dropdown "
"field and two check boxes that control how the text is used in the search."
msgstr ""
"Ta zavihek vam omogoča, da določite besedilo za iskanje. Obstajajo tudi "
"spustno polje in dve potrditveni polji, ki nadzirata, kako se besedilo "
"uporablja pri iskanju."

#. Tag: para
#: details-search.docbook:74
#, no-c-format
msgid "By default, the search will match on simple substrings. For example:"
msgstr "Privzeto se iskanje ujema s preprostimi podnizi. Na primer:"

#. Tag: para
#: details-search.docbook:81
#, no-c-format
msgid "<quote>Best</quote> will find <quote>Best Cakes, Inc.</quote>"
msgstr "<quote>Best</quote> bo našel <quote>Best Cakes, Inc.</quote>"

#. Tag: para
#: details-search.docbook:84
#, no-c-format
msgid "<quote>est</quote> will also find <quote>Best Cakes, Inc.</quote>"
msgstr "<quote>est</quote> bo našel tudi <quote>Best Cakes, Inc.</quote>"

#. Tag: para
#: details-search.docbook:91
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the dropdown field next to the text field, select <guilabel>Contains</"
"guilabel> if you want to find transactions that contain the text, or select "
"<guilabel>Does not contain</guilabel> if you want to find transactions that "
"do not contain the specified text."
msgstr ""
"V spustnem polju poleg besedilnega polja izberite <guilabel>Vsebuje</"
"guilabel>, če želite poiskati transakcije, ki vsebujejo besedilo, ali "
"izberite <guilabel>Ne vsebuje</guilabel>, če želite poiskati transakcije, ki "
"ne vsebujejo navedenega besedila."

#. Tag: para
#: details-search.docbook:98
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you check the <guilabel>Case Sensitive</guilabel> box, the search will be "
"case sensitive. For example, <quote>best</quote> would not find <quote>Best "
"Cakes, Inc.</quote> if this option is set."
msgstr ""
"Če označite polje <guilabel>Razlikuj med velikimi in malimi črkami</"
"guilabel>, bo iskanje občutljivo na velike in male črke. Na primer, "
"<quote>best</quote> ne bi našel <quote>Best Cakes, Inc.</quote>, če je ta "
"možnost nastavljena."

#. Tag: para
#: details-search.docbook:104
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you check the <guilabel>Treat Text as regular expression</guilabel> box, "
"the text will be treated as a regular expression. For details on how to "
"craft a regular expression, visit the &Qt; documentation about the <ulink "
"url=\"https://doc.qt.io/qt-5/qregularexpression.html\">QRegularExpression "
"class</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Če potrdite polje <guilabel>Obravnavaj besedilo kot regularni izraz</"
"guilabel>, bo besedilo obravnavano kot regularni izraz. Za podrobnosti o "
"oblikovanju regularnega izraza obiščite &Qt; dokumentacija o <ulink url="
"\"https://doc.qt.io/qt-5/qregularexpression.html\">razredu "
"QRegularExpression</ulink>."

#. Tag: title
#: details-search.docbook:113
#, no-c-format
msgid "Account"
msgstr "Račun"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: details-search.docbook:115
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<screeninfo>search transactions, criteria tab, account subtab</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>iskanje transakcij, zavihek s kriteriji, podzavihek račun</"
"screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: details-search.docbook:121
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>search transactions, criteria tab, account subtab</phrase>"
msgstr ""
"<phrase>iskanje transakcij, zavihek s kriteriji, podzavihek račun</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: details-search.docbook:126
#, no-c-format
msgid "This tab allows you to specify the accounts that should be searched."
msgstr "Ta zavihek vam omogoča, da določite račune, ki jih je treba preiskati."

#. Tag: para
#: details-search.docbook:130
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Accounts are displayed in a tree format. Accounts that are marked for search "
"are indicated with a checkbox. If you click <guibutton>All</guibutton>, all "
"accounts are marked for searching. If you click <guibutton>None</guibutton>. "
"no accounts will be marked for searching. Individual accounts can be marked "
"or unmarked by clicking the box next to the account name using the &LMB;. A "
"complete hierarchy of accounts can be marked or unmarked by clicking the box "
"using the &RMB;."
msgstr ""
"Računi so prikazani v drevesni obliki. Računi, ki so označeni za iskanje, so "
"označeni s potrditvenim poljem. Če kliknete gumb <guibutton>Vse</guibutton>, "
"so vsi računi označeni za iskanje. Če kliknete gumb <guibutton>Brez</"
"guibutton>, noben račun ne bo označen za iskanje. Posamezne račune lahko "
"označite ali odznačite s klikom na polje poleg imena računa z uporabo &LMB;. "
"Celotno hierarhijo računov je mogoče označiti ali odstraniti s klikom na "
"polje z &RMB;."

#. Tag: title
#: details-search.docbook:140
#, no-c-format
msgid "Date"
msgstr "Datum"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: details-search.docbook:142
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>search transactions, criteria tab, date subtab</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>iskanje transakcij, zavihek kriterijev, podzavihek datum</"
"screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: details-search.docbook:148
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>search transactions, criteria tab, date subtab</phrase>"
msgstr ""
"<phrase>iskanje transakcij, zavihek kriterijev, podzavihek datum</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: details-search.docbook:153
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This tab allows you to specify which dates should be searched. The date "
"refers to the post date of the transaction."
msgstr ""
"Ta zavihek vam omogoča, da določite, katere datume je treba iskati. Datum se "
"nanaša na datum knjiženja transakcije."

#. Tag: para
#: details-search.docbook:158
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <quote>Range</quote> dropdown provides a convenient way to set the From "
"and To date controls. The From and To controls can be manipulated "
"individually. Dates can be entered manually, and clicking the down arrow at "
"the right of the field will bring up a typical calendar widget to select the "
"date. The controls will prevent you from entering non-existing dates. Date "
"values can also be changed by clicking the up and down arrows while the "
"cursor in within a particular part of a date."
msgstr ""
"Spustni meni <quote>Obseg</quote> ponuja priročen način za nastavitev "
"kontrolnikov za datum od in do. S kontrolniki Od in Do je mogoče "
"manipulirati posamično. Datume lahko vnesete ročno in s klikom na puščico "
"navzdol na desni strani polja se prikaže tipičen pripomoček koledarja za "
"izbiro datuma. Kontrolniki vam bodo preprečili vnos neobstoječih datumov. "
"Datumske vrednosti lahko spremenite tudi tako, da kliknete puščici navzgor "
"in navzdol, medtem ko je kazalec znotraj določenega dela datuma."

#. Tag: title
#: details-search.docbook:169
#, no-c-format
msgid "Amount"
msgstr "Znesek"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: details-search.docbook:171
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<screeninfo>search transactions, criteria tab, amount subtab</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>iskanje transakcij, zavihek kriterijev, podzavihek znesek</"
"screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: details-search.docbook:177
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>search transactions, criteria tab, amount subtab</phrase>"
msgstr ""
"<phrase>iskanje transakcij, zavihek kriterijev, podzavihek znesek</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: details-search.docbook:182
#, no-c-format
msgid "This tab allows you to specify what amounts should be searched for."
msgstr "Ta zavihek vam omogoča, da določite, katere zneske je treba iskati."

#. Tag: para
#: details-search.docbook:186
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can search for an exact amount or for a range of amounts. If you click "
"the calculator icon, a small on-screen calculator will pop up to assist you "
"in entering a value."
msgstr ""
"Iščete lahko natančen znesek ali razpon zneskov. Če kliknete ikono "
"kalkulatorja, se prikaže majhen kalkulator na zaslonu, ki vam pomaga pri "
"vnosu vrednosti."

#. Tag: title
#: details-search.docbook:193
#, no-c-format
msgid "Category"
msgstr "Kategorija"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: details-search.docbook:195
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<screeninfo>search transactions, criteria tab, category subtab</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>iskanje transakcij, zavihek kriterijev, podzavihek kategorije</"
"screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: details-search.docbook:201
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>search transactions, criteria tab, category subtab</phrase>"
msgstr ""
"<phrase>iskanje transakcij, zavihek kriterijev, podzavihek kategorije</"
"phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: details-search.docbook:206
#, no-c-format
msgid "This tab allows you to specify which categories should be searched."
msgstr "Ta zavihek vam omogoča, da določite, katere kategorije naj se iščejo."

#. Tag: para
#: details-search.docbook:210
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Categories are displayed in a tree format, similar to Accounts. Categories "
"that are marked for search are indicated with a checkbox. If you click "
"<guibutton>All</guibutton>, all categories are marked for searching. If you "
"click <guibutton>Income</guibutton>, all income categories will be marked "
"and all expense categories will be unmarked. If you click "
"<guibutton>Expense</guibutton>, all income categories will be unmarked and "
"all expense categories will be marked. If you click <guibutton>None</"
"guibutton>, no categories will be marked for searching."
msgstr ""
"Kategorije so prikazane v obliki drevesa, podobno kot računi. Kategorije, ki "
"so označene za iskanje, so označene s potrditvenim poljem. Če kliknete "
"<guibutton>Vse</guibutton>, so vse kategorije označene za iskanje. Če "
"kliknete <guibutton>Dohodek</guibutton>, bodo vse kategorije dohodka "
"označene in vse kategorije odhodkov ne bodo označene. Če kliknete "
"<guibutton>Stroški</guibutton>, bodo vse kategorije prihodkov odznačene in "
"vse kategorije stroškov bodo označene. Če kliknete <guibutton>Brez</"
"guibutton>, nobena kategorija ne bo označena za iskanje."

#. Tag: para
#: details-search.docbook:220
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Individual categories can be marked or unmarked by clicking the checkbox "
"next to the category name using the &LMB;. A complete hierarchy of "
"categories can be marked or unmarked by clicking the box using the &RMB;."
msgstr ""
"Posamezne kategorije lahko označite ali odznačite tako, da z &LMB; kliknete "
"potrditveno polje poleg imena kategorije. Celotno hierarhijo kategorij lahko "
"označite ali odznačite tako, da kliknete polje z &RMB;."

#. Tag: title
#: details-search.docbook:227
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Tag</title>"
msgstr "<title>Značka</title>"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: details-search.docbook:229
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>search transactions, criteria tab, tag subtab</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>iskanje transakcij, zavihek kriterijev, podzavihek značke</"
"screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: details-search.docbook:235
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>search transactions, criteria tab, tag subtab</phrase>"
msgstr ""
"<phrase>iskanje transakcij, zavihek kriterijev, podzavihek značke</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: details-search.docbook:240
#, no-c-format
msgid "This tab allows you to specify which tags should be searched."
msgstr "Ta zavihek vam omogoča določiti, katere značke naj se iščejo."

#. Tag: para
#: details-search.docbook:244
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Tags that are marked for search are indicated with a checked box. If you "
"click <guibutton>Select all</guibutton>, all tags are marked for searching. "
"If you click <guibutton>Select none</guibutton>, no tags will be marked for "
"searching. Individual tags can be marked or unmarked by clicking the "
"checkbox next to the payee name."
msgstr ""
"Značke, ki so označene za iskanje, so označene s potrjenim poljem. Če "
"kliknete <guibutton>Izberi vse</guibutton>, so vse značke označene za "
"iskanje. Če kliknete <guibutton>Izberi nič</guibutton>, nobene značke ne bo "
"označene za iskanje. Posamezne značke lahko označite ali odznačite tako, da "
"kliknete potrditveno polje poleg imena prejemnika plačila."

#. Tag: para
#: details-search.docbook:252
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you check the <guilabel>Select transactions without tags</guilabel> box, "
"only transactions with no tag will be selected."
msgstr ""
"Če označite polje <guilabel>Izberi transakcije brez značk</guilabel>, bodo "
"izbrane samo transakcije brez značk."

#. Tag: title
#: details-search.docbook:258
#, no-c-format
msgid "Payee"
msgstr "Prejemnik plačila"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: details-search.docbook:260
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<screeninfo>search transactions, criteria tab, payee subtab</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>iskanje transakcij, zavihek s kriteriji, podzavihek prejemnik</"
"screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: details-search.docbook:266
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>search transactions, criteria tab, payee subtab</phrase>"
msgstr ""
"<phrase>iskanje transakcij, zavihek s kriteriji, podzavihek prejemnik</"
"phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: details-search.docbook:271
#, no-c-format
msgid "This tab allows you to specify which payees should be searched."
msgstr ""
"Ta zavihek vam omogoča, da določite, katere prejemnike plačil je treba "
"iskati."

#. Tag: para
#: details-search.docbook:275
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Payees that are marked for search are indicated with a box. If you click "
"<guibutton>Select all</guibutton>, all payees are marked for searching. If "
"you click <guibutton>Select none</guibutton>, no payees will be marked for "
"searching. Individual payees can be marked or unmarked by clicking the box "
"next to the payee name."
msgstr ""
"Prejemniki plačil, ki so označeni za iskanje, so označeni s kvadratkom. Če "
"kliknete <guibutton>Izberi vse</guibutton>, so vsi prejemniki plačil "
"označeni za iskanje. Če kliknete <guibutton>Izberi nobenega</guibutton>, "
"noben prejemnik ne bo označen za iskanje. Posamezne prejemnike lahko "
"označite ali odznačite tako, da kliknete polje poleg imena prejemnika."

#. Tag: para
#: details-search.docbook:283
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you check the <guilabel>Select transactions without payees</guilabel> "
"box, only transactions with no payee will be selected."
msgstr ""
"Če potrdite polje <guilabel>Izberi transakcije brez prejemnikov</guilabel>, "
"bodo izbrane samo transakcije brez prejemnikov plačil."

#. Tag: title
#: details-search.docbook:289
#, no-c-format
msgid "Details"
msgstr "Podrobnosti"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: details-search.docbook:291
#, no-c-format
msgid "search transactions, criteria tab, details subtab"
msgstr "iskanje transakcij, zavihek kriterijev, podzavihek podrobnosti"

#. Tag: phrase
#: details-search.docbook:297
#, no-c-format
msgid "Search transactions Dialog, Details tab"
msgstr "Pogovorno okno za iskanje transakcij, zavihek s podrobnostmi"

#. Tag: para
#: details-search.docbook:302
#, no-c-format
msgid "This tab allows you to specify various additional search criteria."
msgstr ""
"Ta zavihek vam omogoča, da določite različne dodatne iskalne kriterije."

#. Tag: title
#: details-search.docbook:308
#, no-c-format
msgid "Type can be one of the following:"
msgstr "Vrsta je lahko ena od naslednjih:"

#. Tag: para
#: details-search.docbook:309
#, no-c-format
msgid "All Types"
msgstr "Vse vrste"

#. Tag: para
#: details-search.docbook:310
#, no-c-format
msgid "Payments"
msgstr "Plačila"

#. Tag: para
#: details-search.docbook:311
#, no-c-format
msgid "Deposits"
msgstr "Depoziti"

#. Tag: para
#: details-search.docbook:312
#, no-c-format
msgid "Transfers"
msgstr "Prestopi"

#. Tag: title
#: details-search.docbook:316
#, no-c-format
msgid "State can be one of the following:"
msgstr "Stanje je lahko eno od naslednjega:"

#. Tag: para
#: details-search.docbook:317
#, no-c-format
msgid "All states"
msgstr "Vse države"

#. Tag: para
#: details-search.docbook:318
#, no-c-format
msgid "Not reconciled"
